<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL9">
<l>maṟṟumōr teyva muṇṭē matiyilā māṉi ṭaṅkā</l>
<l>ḷuṟṟapō taṉṟi nīṅka ḷoruvaṉeṉ ṟuṇara māṭṭī</l>
<l>raṟṟamē loṉṟa ṟīyīra vaṉallāl teyva millai</l>
<l>kaṟṟiṉam mēytta ventai kaḻaliṇai paṇimi ṉīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O humans devoid of discernment! Is there any another God?</l>
<l>You will not realise that [He is] the [only] One except when you suffer!</l>
<l>You do not know anything about the superior, concealed [Entity]: there is no God but Him.</l>
<l>Humble yourselves at the pair of ankleted [feet] of my Father who grazed herds of calves!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
